latestPosts.caption:
Had every reason to quit. But we didn’t.

One month of Hyrox prep — side by side — while also training for a 21km marathon.

We hit wall after wall but kept showing up✍🏻 as this was never about being the best. It was about getting better & stronger together.

And when we crossed that finish line at 1:23:04 exhausted, hurting, proud we knew it was worth every step.🏅

Shoutout to @shubh_am.17 for capturing the snapshots and @aayush_sawdawkar for the physio support

Special thanks to our training venue partners @ileseum.clubs @rahejadistrictarena.ileseum 

This is what heart looks like @healthustleclub 🫀

Kudos to everyone who gave their all and finished the job🙌🏻

#hyrox #hyroxindia #healthandhustle #hyroxtraining🏃🏻‍♂️
